** Give a Sorted Array And a Number x, Such Two Elements Of The Array Such That Their Sum Is x. EXPECTED TIME COMPLEXITY O(n).

def find_pair (arr, x):
  left = 0
  right = len (arr) - 1
  while left < right :
    current_sum = arr[left] + arr[right]
    if current_sum == x:
      return arr[left], arr[right]
    elif current_sum < x :
      left += 1
    else :
      right -= 1
    return None
